- ‚úÖ **Data Accuracy**: Portfolio calculations within 0.01% precision
- ‚úÖ **User Experience**: Complete workflows without errors

### **Advanced Features:**
- ‚úÖ **AI Strategy Performance**: >15% annual returns in backtesting
- ‚úÖ **Risk Management**: Real-time monitoring with <1 second alerts
- ‚úÖ **Market Intelligence**: News analysis with >80% sentiment accuracy
- ‚úÖ **Portfolio Optimization**: Sharpe ratio improvements >20%

### **Business Metrics:**
- ‚úÖ **User Retention**: >90% of users complete onboarding
